    'IN' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Revolutionizing E-commerce for Indian Merchants with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>In the vibrant markets of India, where tradition meets innovation, Selldone Business OS is ushering in a new era of e-commerce. This no-plugin platform is tailored for Indian merchants, offering a seamless avenue to sell products, services, subscriptions, and even files.</p>\n\n<h3>Establish Your Digital Presence</h3>\n<p>Indian businesses can now carve out their unique space on the internet. With Selldone, your e-commerce platform resides on your chosen domain, ensuring a genuine connection with every visitor.</p>\n\n<h3>Uncomplicated Beginnings</h3>\n<p>Launching an online store in India shouldn't be tangled in complexities. Selldone ensures that merchants can set up with ease, eliminating the need for hosting, plugins, or templates. It's about making e-commerce straightforward and accessible.</p>\n\n<h3>Compliant with India's Tax System</h3>\n<p>India's tax landscape is intricate, but Selldone is up to the task. With integrated tax calculation features, it ensures that businesses navigate the nuances of local taxation effortlessly.</p>\n\n<h3>Scaling with India's Ambitious Brands</h3>\n<p>From startups in Bengaluru to established brands in Mumbai, Selldone is designed to grow alongside Indian businesses. It's the e-commerce partner for those with a vision.</p>\n\n<h3>Conversion at its Core</h3>\n<p>Selldone isn't just about selling; it's about maximizing every opportunity. Crafted for the Indian market, it's optimized to turn visitors into loyal customers.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the Indian Shopper</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate festive shopping sprees.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to captivate the diverse Indian audience.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to enhance the value of every cart.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those special gifting moments.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing for the Indian Audience</h3>\n<p>Reaching out to India's vast and varied audience is a breeze with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about creating lasting bonds in the world's largest democracy.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-commerce Standards in India</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might present challenges with hosting and a fragmented user experience, Selldone offers a cohesive and intuitive journey for both merchants and shoppers.</p>\n\n<h3>Surpassing Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come with their set of challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can disrupt the shopping experience.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> with numerous plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering Indian merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce journey.</p>\n\n<p>For the merchants of India, Selldone Business OS is more than just a platform; it's the future of e-commerce. Dive in and experience the difference.</p>\n"],
